    <dashboard name='S&amp;P 500 Financial Analysis | Takeaways' type='storyboard'>
      <style>
        <style-rule element='story-description'>
          <format attr='background-color' id='story-description_6' value='#ffffffd9' />
          <format attr='border-width' id='story-description_6' value='0' />
          <format attr='border-style' id='story-description_6' value='none' />
        </style-rule>
      </style>
      <size maxheight='825' maxwidth='1250' minheight='825' minwidth='1250' sizing-mode='fixed' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='2' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='98060' id='1' param='vert' removable='false' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98720' x='640' y='970'>
            <zone h='4000' id='3' type-v2='title' w='98720' x='640' y='970' />
            <zone h='7636' id='4' paired-zone-id='5' removable='false' type-v2='flipboard-nav' w='98720' x='640' y='4970' />
            <zone h='86424' id='5' paired-zone-id='4' removable='false' type-v2='flipboard' w='98720' x='640' y='12606'>
              <flipboard active-id='1' nav-type='dot' show-nav-arrows='true'>
                <story-points>
                  <story-point captured-sheet='' id='1' />
                </story-points>
              </flipboard>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='61455' id='6' story-point-id='1' type-v2='text' w='82000' x='9040' y='11758'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>This dashboard analyzes S&amp;P 500 performance from 2022 to 2025 across three key questions.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Which sectors generated the strongest returns?</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Æ </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Information Technology led all sectors with the highest average daily return at approximately 4.4%. Real Estate and Consumer Staples were the only two sectors to average a net loss over the period.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Which sectors saw the most trading activity?</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Æ </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Information Technology again led the other sectors, recording average daily trading volume more than double that of the next closest sector. This level of activity suggests that investors were more engaged with technology stocks throughout this period compared to any other sector. </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Which stocks offered the best return relative to their risk?</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Æ </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>The data shows that the majority of S&amp;P 500 stocks were relatively stable, clustering within a low average daily price range. The stocks that combined positive returns with lower volatility were largely concentrated in the Technology and Communication Services sectors, while stocks with higher volatility did not necessarily produce proportionally higher returns.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='2'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='2' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11' italic='true'>Data sourced from Yahoo Finance via yfinance and Wikipedia S&amp;P 500 Constituents List.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
      <simple-id uuid='{8DF7A85C-726F-4097-9469-A1E28010BB97}' />
    </dashboard>
